{"tid":639854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我睇到篇文章叫在中國年薪不過百萬如何生活","createTime":"2018-04-23T22:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T22:35:30.000Z","uid":165772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d75f55cef0e86f89507c649159f9dfeaba07201b","tid":639854,"uid":165772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T22:35:30.000Z","msg":"戴左頭盔先 一個朋友俾我既<br />\n年薪百萬以下生活唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要人仔結算 除0.8x  家庭計都人均月薪5萬港幣<br />\n<br />\n版权归作者所有，任何形式转载请联系作者。<br />\n作者：浪潮工作室（来自豆瓣）<br />\n来源：<a href=\"https://www.douban.com/note/663699632/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.douban.com%2Fnote%2F663699632%2F&d=pbWIAD41y6BH%2FlEbXVH6Xf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=0e7c12f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.douban.com/note/663699632/</a><br />\n<br />\n每天，数以亿计的中国人为支撑大大小小的家庭而往返奔波在赚钱的路上，梦想着为自己和家人带来更好的生活。而在社交网络上，且不说知乎用户纷纷宣称自己年入千万，就连百万年薪也被不少微博用户认为在北京这样的城市属于&ldquo;刚刚脱贫&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n我们明明在同一个国家，却像生活在完全不同的世界。那么普通中国人一年到底能挣多少钱呢？<br />\n<br />\n根据国家统计局数据，2017年，中国居民人均可支配收入仅为25974元，若看中位数则只有22408元，所以一个全员工作的三口之家的年收入应该在6、7万元上下。而在西南财经大学发布的《2017中国工薪阶层信贷发展报告》中，除去了收入较低的农村后，中国工薪阶层家庭年均收入也只有15.4万元而已。<br />\n<br />\n比社交网络中&ldquo;赤贫&rdquo;阶层还不如的普通中国家庭，是怎么生活的呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/062813_07a78293739a8f8b851260a4f0c216ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F062813_07a78293739a8f8b851260a4f0c216ec.png&h=3018a4ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/062816_f6584bad629c5489d92773bcae7913b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F062816_f6584bad629c5489d92773bcae7913b1.png&h=5fe4107b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/062818_a83e4e58e5313a6e9360c927abcc2597.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F062818_a83e4e58e5313a6e9360c927abcc2597.png&h=2cb90e37&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/062824_4bc8260092cd91b8bdc545faa98a4bac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F062824_4bc8260092cd91b8bdc545faa98a4bac.png&h=b3e540e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/062826_ad45f60f66945119c1bf1745783b4e8b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F062826_ad45f60f66945119c1bf1745783b4e8b.png&h=a141d677&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/062831_8a957e90b8269356b32e5a85c0378b5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F062831_8a957e90b8269356b32e5a85c0378b5b.png&h=7eedaa7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/062834_430e921f01b2c5c52b713472481f6427.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F062834_430e921f01b2c5c52b713472481f6427.png&h=f31836a0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}